                    <span>This is one of the few books that I have read over and over again. You find a lot of valuable resources and it is a very entertaining read. I always find something new. Being a succesfull trader, I recomend this book to anybody that is interested in this bussines.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An important book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>6</span>
